  "remarks": "Precise Electro-Mechanics Plant is a Belarusian State enterprise that specializes in the development and production of military products and subordinate to the State Military-Industrial Committee of the Republic of Belarus. In this capacity Precise Electro-Mechanics Plant produces military hardware in use by the Belarus armed forces, notably ballistic missiles and provides revenue to the Belarusian State.",
